NAME:
	bashgpt - Integration between chatgpt and bash terminal

CREATORS:
	Kshitij Saxena, Rajat Govil, Yashasvi Khare, Sparsh Kaudinya, Hashim

SYNOPSIS:
	bashgpt [DOMAIN] "QUESTION"
	bashgpt CTSSUM [OPTIONS] [FILE...]
	bashgpt DRCSUM [OPTIONS] [FILE...]
	bashgpt [INFO]
DESCRIPTION: 
	This Project attempts to integrate the functionality of chatgpt to the bash terminal along with the added usability of CTS log file and DRC file summarizer.
	bashgpt asks the QUESTION under the DOMAIN specified from chatgpt and outputs it onto the terminal.

INFO:
	--help 
		Output a usage message and exit.
	
	-V, --version
		Outputs the version number of bashgpt and exit.
	
	-m, --maxtokens=NUM
		GPT responses will be of maximum NUM words.
	-h, --history
		Displays the past 5 questions and their responses.		
CTSSUM:
	Cts Log File Summerizer
	OPTIONS:
		-1
			Outputs 
		-2
			Outputs
		-3
			Ouputs

DRCSUM:
	Drc File Summerizer
	OPTIONS:
		-1
			Outputs 
		-2
			Outputs
		-3
			Ouputs

